name: Ana Rodrigues (@ohhelloana@mastodon.social)
summary:
I spent part of my evening working on my website's "speaking" page. I reviewed the archive and found nice things people said about those talks and photos, and it made me quite teary. 

I was so harsh on myself then, but now I look back to the person I was in 2018 and 2019... I was just a baby. How hopeful I was in those talks. Oh my...
